{
  "stem": "1343.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we wanted to go back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They put us on a train, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but I have to go back again for one more moment.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On the day of the liberation in Gunskirchen, it was late afternoon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was still dusk, but you could still see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All of a sudden, we saw those Sonderkommando children because they were still in the striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were running into the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One had a [NON-ENGLISH], but her leg was still in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A German [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But her leg was still in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Another one with her torso.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the sergeant from Mauthausen, so that was the only, only [NON-ENGLISH], the revenge that I have seen that was taken.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, I should say that the next day, when the Americans came in, they gathered some of the SS-- former SS guards who were hiding in the forests.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They caught them, but they were already in civilian suits.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they had the tattoo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the SS had a tattoo on their arms with the death head.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they gathered them, and they were slapping the corpses into the mass graves, like we used to, before.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I saw, with my own eyes, that some of the Americans did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They kicked them into the grave, like they used to do with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we did not realize then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, there was no thinking, and no rationalizing, no logic, no rhyme, reason-- only instinct.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were afraid of them because they were strong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if we had any food and they saw it, they grabbed it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But these were people who were dehumanized to the maximum.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went back.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
